.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-7-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, cherry, apricot, grapes
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: golfd-games, mystery, crime, family
4 different games are played: whist, bridge, poker, canasta
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, may, april, february
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, yellow, fuchsia, grey
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, weightlifting, biathlon, handball
 1. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
 2. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 3. the person watching family movies is the person playing whist##1
 4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 5. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
 8. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching golfd-games movies is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
11. the person who likes yellow is the person who's sport is golf##1
12. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the right of the person who likes fuchsia##5
13. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
14. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
15. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person eating grapes and the person who's birthday is in february##7
16. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
17. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
18. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
19. the person eating grapes is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
20. the person who likes grey is in an odd position##4
21. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |      3      |      4      |
| Food      | cherry  | grapes          | apricot       | pumpkin         |
| Movie-Genre         | mystery | crime      | family | golfd-games  |
| Game           | poker  | canasta | whist       | bridge |
